{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10355627 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9786180 (ii) The difficulty of lorry drivers, etc., sent for short visits, in finding accommodation on the journey or at the end. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10355627 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9786180 (iii) "The exploitation of women workers at lower wages than men".
