\par It is suggested in London that "the Communist Party is putting about that it was they who got the rise in Army pay put through".
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10030560 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9786180 High wages; The high wages of "younger people" still appear to be causing concern; it is felt that there should be some system of compulsory saving for them.
\par 
\par In the North Midland Region there are said to be "many people who view with alarm the advances in wages which are being granted to certain trades, and who are wondering when this business of 'dog chasing tail' will stop".
